quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  26,20,"Qala faAAaltuha ithanwaana mina addalleen"
  26,21,"Fafarartu minkum lamma khiftukumfawahaba lee rabbee hukman wajaAAalanee mina almursaleen"
  26,22,"Watilka niAAmatun tamunnuha AAalayyaan AAabbadta banee isra-eel"
  26,23,"Qala firAAawnu wama rabbu alAAalameen"
  26,24,"Qala rabbu assamawatiwal-ardi wama baynahuma in kuntummooqineen"
  26,25,"Qala liman hawlahu alatastamiAAoon"
  26,26,"Qala rabbukum warabbu aba-ikumual-awwaleen"
  26,27,"Qala inna rasoolakumu allatheeorsila ilaykum lamajnoon"
  26,28,"Qala rabbu almashriqi walmaghribiwama baynahuma in kuntum taAAqiloon"
  26,29,"Qala la-ini ittakhathta ilahanghayree laajAAalannaka mina almasjooneen"
  26,30,"Qala awa law ji/tuka bishay-in mubeen"
  26,31,"Qala fa/ti bihi in kunta mina assadiqeen"
  26,32,"Faalqa AAasahu fa-ithahiya thuAAbanun mubeen"
  26,33,"WanazaAAa yadahu fa-itha hiya baydaolinnathireen"
  26,34,"Qala lilmala-i hawlahu inna hathalasahirun AAaleem"
  26,35,"Yureedu an yukhrijakum min ardikumbisihrihi famatha ta/muroon"
  26,36,"Qaloo arjih waakhahu wabAAathfee almada-ini hashireen"
  26,37,"Ya/tooka bikulli sahharin AAaleem"
  26,38,"FajumiAAa assaharatu limeeqatiyawmin maAAloom"
  26,39,"Waqeela linnasi hal antummujtamiAAoon"
